"and :method:`db.collection.findAndModify()`,"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/reference/operator/update/positional.txt:44
msgid ""
"the positional :update:`$` operator acts as a placeholder for the "
"**first** element that matches the ``query document``, and"
msgstr ""

